<article class="indiv-product">

  <script type="application/json" id="product-grid-7372762611861" class="product-grid-json">
    {"id":7372762611861,"title":"February: Flatter Me","handle":"february-flatter-me","description":"\u003cp\u003eGet ready with this box that has all of your date-night essentials. Begin with a rich glow cream; get your oral hygiene on with a standalone bamboo toothbrush; create a unique eye-do with a fun-and-flirty eyeshadow and a sultry black liner; and spray on an elegant, sexy, and alluring scent for the perfect finishing touch. Then, get ready for compliments.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eInkling Scents: Poppy Fields Roll-On\u003c\/strong\u003e ($25 value) \u003cbr\u003eSensual, youthful, and long-lasting, this scent achieves a delicate balance between bright notes like cucumber and mandarin and sultry and sexy crème brulée and cedarwood, leaving you feeling effervescent, feminine, and floral. The roll-on applicator and compact size make this scent perfect to pop into your purse for anytime wear.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDelia Organics: Goji Glow Cream\u003c\/strong\u003e ($19.40 value) \u003cbr\u003eGlow up for a hot date out or a peaceful night in. This non-greasy, fast-absorbing cream will make you feel like a million bucks morning or night. Black goji berries deliver amino acids to your skin, while vanilla and lavender provide a luscious scent. This cream hydrates, tones, and is a “berry” good way to treat yourself!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eEstate Cosmetics: Just A Taste Eyeshadow Palette in On Wednesdays\u003c\/strong\u003e ($14 value) \u003cbr\u003eThe color of love. These eyeshadow color quads include neutrals perfect for everyday wear plus a pop of red that will bring you all the adoration. Letting you choose between matte and shimmery finishes, these pretty palettes are blendable, long-lasting, and perfect for any type of date.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e100% Pure: Creamy Long Last Liner in Blackest\u003c\/strong\u003e ($26 value) \u003cbr\u003eThis buttery-soft pencil liner will define your eyes in comfort and style. Made with jojoba oil, chamomile butter, and mango seed oil, this stunning liner will nourish your skin while delivering a seamless, flake-free application. With this deep, inky black color to make your eyes pop, you definitely won’t be fading into the night.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePanga: Black Bamboo Toothbrush\u003c\/strong\u003e ($6.49 value) \u003cbr\u003eSupport your oral health with this toothbrush that doesn’t need anyone to lean on. Made of biodegradable bamboo and BPA-free nylon bristles, this brush will have your pearly whites shining. With a black base so you can tell whose is whose, this brush will stand up on its own—no caddy necessary. We give this one a standing ovation!\u003c\/p\u003e","published_at":"2022-02-17T07:41:42-07:00","created_at":"2022-02-17T07:41:27-07:00","vendor":"Kinder Beauty ","type":"","tags":[],"price":2400,"price_min":2400,"price_max":2400,"available":false,"price_varies":false,"compare_at_price":9089,"compare_at_price_min":9089,"compare_at_price_max":9089,"compare_at_price_varies":false,"variants":[{"id":41932783485077,"title":"Default Title","option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"sku":"","requires_shipping":true,"taxable":true,"featured_image":null,"available":false,"name":"February: Flatter Me","public_title":null,"options":["Default Title"],"price":2400,"weight":0,"compare_at_price":9089,"inventory_management":"shopify","barcode":"","requires_selling_plan":false,"selling_plan_allocations":[]}],"images":["\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/FlatterMeBox_1500x_ea369672-b704-4f7d-ba8d-02aa93f1c59c.jpg?v=1645109035","\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/InklingScents-PoppyFields_1500x_bb13a262-dbab-4fd1-8ae6-fb469d2ea546.jpg?v=1645109029","\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/DeliaOrganics-GojiGlowCream_1500x_57b54742-bb42-4caa-a354-c8d98553c47d.jpg?v=1645109023","\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/EstateCosmetics-JustaTasteQuadsinOnWednesday_1500x_5ea6fda1-2990-4cda-aaec-72eab121e5ee.jpg?v=1645109018","\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/100PercentPure-CreamyLongLastLingerinBlackest_1500x_6e96e293-eed6-4916-bf86-9b676adbe72f.jpg?v=1645109011","\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/PangaBambooToothbrushblack_1500x_c4248c24-9331-4bf1-9014-ef325f016288.jpg?v=1645109006"],"featured_image":"\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/FlatterMeBox_1500x_ea369672-b704-4f7d-ba8d-02aa93f1c59c.jpg?v=1645109035","options":["Title"],"media":[{"alt":null,"id":26175493734549,"position":1,"preview_image":{"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":650,"width":650,"src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/FlatterMeBox_1500x_ea369672-b704-4f7d-ba8d-02aa93f1c59c.jpg?v=1645109035"},"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":650,"media_type":"image","src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/FlatterMeBox_1500x_ea369672-b704-4f7d-ba8d-02aa93f1c59c.jpg?v=1645109035","width":650},{"alt":null,"id":26175493767317,"position":2,"preview_image":{"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":550,"width":550,"src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/InklingScents-PoppyFields_1500x_bb13a262-dbab-4fd1-8ae6-fb469d2ea546.jpg?v=1645109029"},"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":550,"media_type":"image","src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/InklingScents-PoppyFields_1500x_bb13a262-dbab-4fd1-8ae6-fb469d2ea546.jpg?v=1645109029","width":550},{"alt":null,"id":26175493800085,"position":3,"preview_image":{"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":550,"width":550,"src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/DeliaOrganics-GojiGlowCream_1500x_57b54742-bb42-4caa-a354-c8d98553c47d.jpg?v=1645109023"},"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":550,"media_type":"image","src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/DeliaOrganics-GojiGlowCream_1500x_57b54742-bb42-4caa-a354-c8d98553c47d.jpg?v=1645109023","width":550},{"alt":null,"id":26175493832853,"position":4,"preview_image":{"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":550,"width":550,"src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/EstateCosmetics-JustaTasteQuadsinOnWednesday_1500x_5ea6fda1-2990-4cda-aaec-72eab121e5ee.jpg?v=1645109018"},"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":550,"media_type":"image","src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/EstateCosmetics-JustaTasteQuadsinOnWednesday_1500x_5ea6fda1-2990-4cda-aaec-72eab121e5ee.jpg?v=1645109018","width":550},{"alt":null,"id":26175493865621,"position":5,"preview_image":{"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":550,"width":550,"src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/100PercentPure-CreamyLongLastLingerinBlackest_1500x_6e96e293-eed6-4916-bf86-9b676adbe72f.jpg?v=1645109011"},"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":550,"media_type":"image","src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/100PercentPure-CreamyLongLastLingerinBlackest_1500x_6e96e293-eed6-4916-bf86-9b676adbe72f.jpg?v=1645109011","width":550},{"alt":null,"id":26175493898389,"position":6,"preview_image":{"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":550,"width":550,"src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/PangaBambooToothbrushblack_1500x_c4248c24-9331-4bf1-9014-ef325f016288.jpg?v=1645109006"},"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":550,"media_type":"image","src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/PangaBambooToothbrushblack_1500x_c4248c24-9331-4bf1-9014-ef325f016288.jpg?v=1645109006","width":550}],"requires_selling_plan":false,"selling_plan_groups":[],"content":"\u003cp\u003eGet ready with this box that has all of your date-night essentials. Begin with a rich glow cream; get your oral hygiene on with a standalone bamboo toothbrush; create a unique eye-do with a fun-and-flirty eyeshadow and a sultry black liner; and spray on an elegant, sexy, and alluring scent for the perfect finishing touch. Then, get ready for compliments.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eInkling Scents: Poppy Fields Roll-On\u003c\/strong\u003e ($25 value) \u003cbr\u003eSensual, youthful, and long-lasting, this scent achieves a delicate balance between bright notes like cucumber and mandarin and sultry and sexy crème brulée and cedarwood, leaving you feeling effervescent, feminine, and floral. The roll-on applicator and compact size make this scent perfect to pop into your purse for anytime wear.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDelia Organics: Goji Glow Cream\u003c\/strong\u003e ($19.40 value) \u003cbr\u003eGlow up for a hot date out or a peaceful night in. This non-greasy, fast-absorbing cream will make you feel like a million bucks morning or night. Black goji berries deliver amino acids to your skin, while vanilla and lavender provide a luscious scent. This cream hydrates, tones, and is a “berry” good way to treat yourself!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eEstate Cosmetics: Just A Taste Eyeshadow Palette in On Wednesdays\u003c\/strong\u003e ($14 value) \u003cbr\u003eThe color of love. These eyeshadow color quads include neutrals perfect for everyday wear plus a pop of red that will bring you all the adoration. Letting you choose between matte and shimmery finishes, these pretty palettes are blendable, long-lasting, and perfect for any type of date.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e100% Pure: Creamy Long Last Liner in Blackest\u003c\/strong\u003e ($26 value) \u003cbr\u003eThis buttery-soft pencil liner will define your eyes in comfort and style. Made with jojoba oil, chamomile butter, and mango seed oil, this stunning liner will nourish your skin while delivering a seamless, flake-free application. With this deep, inky black color to make your eyes pop, you definitely won’t be fading into the night.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePanga: Black Bamboo Toothbrush\u003c\/strong\u003e ($6.49 value) \u003cbr\u003eSupport your oral health with this toothbrush that doesn’t need anyone to lean on. Made of biodegradable bamboo and BPA-free nylon bristles, this brush will have your pearly whites shining. With a black base so you can tell whose is whose, this brush will stand up on its own—no caddy necessary. We give this one a standing ovation!\u003c\/p\u003e"}
