<article class="indiv-product">

  <script type="application/json" id="product-grid-7372757106837" class="product-grid-json">
    {"id":7372757106837,"title":"January Box: Fresh Start","handle":"january-box-fresh-start","description":"\u003cp\u003eNew year, new you, new skin routine! Kickstart 2022 with perfect-for-you products designed to keep your darling skin moisture-rich and glowy. In the Fresh Start box, you’ll find a hydrating oil serum, a toner that will give you a dewy complexion, a mask featuring hyaluronic acid as the superstar ingredient, a powerful vitamin C eye serum, and a creamy matte blush to give a subtle sheen to your ultra-hydrated skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFranklin \u0026amp; Whitman: Vitamin C Eye Serum\u003c\/strong\u003e ($39.95 value) \u003cbr\u003eNot all heroes wear capes. If you’ve got dark under-eye circles, then this serum is to the rescue with a concentrated vitamin C formula that reduces discoloration over time and boosts the appearance of collagen-rich skin. Powerhouse ingredients like moringa oil join the action to soothe while squalane smooths out fine lines.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eJubel Naturals: Daily Dew\u003c\/strong\u003e ($34 value) \u003cbr\u003eGive your skin its daily due of hydration with a luxurious blend of nutrient-rich oils formulated for skin on the drier side (but works great for all skin types, too). A dollop a day of this subtly-scented elixir will give you a supple glow, leaving your skin fresh as morning dew.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eRosatyque: Hyaluronic Acid Moisturizing Mask\u003c\/strong\u003e ($6 value) \u003cbr\u003eDip into the fountain of youth with this hydrating mask. Hyaluronic acid helps skin retain moisture while astragalus membranaceus root extract turns back the clock with its revered age-defying properties. Formulated to also address eczema, rashes, plus deliver a dose of antioxidants, this mask is a great use of your time and money.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSukin: Hydrating Mist Toner\u003c\/strong\u003e ($2.99) \u003cbr\u003eYou lead a busy life, and so does your skin. With this mist toner you can give your skin a little pick me up any time of the day or night. Chamomile and rosewater soothe and purify tired skin, and a couple spritzes after makeup application will give you a dewy complexion. Don’t spend another day without it.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePeek Beauty: Metalimatte Quick Drying Blush\u003c\/strong\u003e ($18.50 value) \u003cbr\u003eThink you can’t be subtle and striking all at once? Think again with this blush that gives you the best of all worlds. Starting as a smooth matte cream that finishes as a gorgeous powder, this blush, in shade Ku, is blended with a touch of metallic shimmer to give the perfect light to your look.\u003c\/p\u003e","published_at":"2022-02-17T07:29:26-07:00","created_at":"2022-02-17T07:29:25-07:00","vendor":"Kinder Beauty ","type":"","tags":[],"price":2400,"price_min":2400,"price_max":2400,"available":false,"price_varies":false,"compare_at_price":10144,"compare_at_price_min":10144,"compare_at_price_max":10144,"compare_at_price_varies":false,"variants":[{"id":41932758646933,"title":"Default Title","option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"sku":"","requires_shipping":true,"taxable":true,"featured_image":null,"available":false,"name":"January Box: Fresh Start","public_title":null,"options":["Default Title"],"price":2400,"weight":0,"compare_at_price":10144,"inventory_management":"shopify","barcode":"","requires_selling_plan":false,"selling_plan_allocations":[]}],"images":["\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/jan2022-hero.jpg?v=1645108317","\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/fresh-start-franklin-whitman-vit-c-eye-serum_1500x_1b6e66d0-16af-40d4-b2d2-ce78158021cd.png?v=1645108308","\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/jubel-natural-daily-dew_1500x_ef77f2d5-74bd-4cd8-8433-86b730e6bab3.png?v=1645108305","\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/rosatyque-hyaluronic-acid-sheet-mask_1500x_ecaa2df3-2a6d-496e-8b03-9e128357726c.png?v=1645108297","\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/peek-beauty-metalimatte-blush_1500x_c827f29c-b9e1-4e27-8e7b-fa8f34dd94d7.png?v=1645108290","\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/sukin-hydrating-mist-toner_1500x_dc39d8a0-bdbf-463b-8dcf-d493f83e885a.png?v=1645108285"],"featured_image":"\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/jan2022-hero.jpg?v=1645108317","options":["Title"],"media":[{"alt":null,"id":26175440715925,"position":1,"preview_image":{"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":1500,"width":1500,"src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/jan2022-hero.jpg?v=1645108317"},"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":1500,"media_type":"image","src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/jan2022-hero.jpg?v=1645108317","width":1500},{"alt":null,"id":26175440748693,"position":2,"preview_image":{"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":638,"width":638,"src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/fresh-start-franklin-whitman-vit-c-eye-serum_1500x_1b6e66d0-16af-40d4-b2d2-ce78158021cd.png?v=1645108308"},"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":638,"media_type":"image","src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/fresh-start-franklin-whitman-vit-c-eye-serum_1500x_1b6e66d0-16af-40d4-b2d2-ce78158021cd.png?v=1645108308","width":638},{"alt":null,"id":26175440781461,"position":3,"preview_image":{"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":765,"width":765,"src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/jubel-natural-daily-dew_1500x_ef77f2d5-74bd-4cd8-8433-86b730e6bab3.png?v=1645108305"},"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":765,"media_type":"image","src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/jubel-natural-daily-dew_1500x_ef77f2d5-74bd-4cd8-8433-86b730e6bab3.png?v=1645108305","width":765},{"alt":null,"id":26175440814229,"position":4,"preview_image":{"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":765,"width":765,"src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/rosatyque-hyaluronic-acid-sheet-mask_1500x_ecaa2df3-2a6d-496e-8b03-9e128357726c.png?v=1645108297"},"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":765,"media_type":"image","src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/rosatyque-hyaluronic-acid-sheet-mask_1500x_ecaa2df3-2a6d-496e-8b03-9e128357726c.png?v=1645108297","width":765},{"alt":null,"id":26175440846997,"position":5,"preview_image":{"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":765,"width":765,"src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/peek-beauty-metalimatte-blush_1500x_c827f29c-b9e1-4e27-8e7b-fa8f34dd94d7.png?v=1645108290"},"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":765,"media_type":"image","src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/peek-beauty-metalimatte-blush_1500x_c827f29c-b9e1-4e27-8e7b-fa8f34dd94d7.png?v=1645108290","width":765},{"alt":null,"id":26175440879765,"position":6,"preview_image":{"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":765,"width":765,"src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/sukin-hydrating-mist-toner_1500x_dc39d8a0-bdbf-463b-8dcf-d493f83e885a.png?v=1645108285"},"aspect_ratio":1.0,"height":765,"media_type":"image","src":"https:\/\/web.archive.org\/web\/20220227111207\/https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0118\/0631\/0459\/products\/sukin-hydrating-mist-toner_1500x_dc39d8a0-bdbf-463b-8dcf-d493f83e885a.png?v=1645108285","width":765}],"requires_selling_plan":false,"selling_plan_groups":[],"content":"\u003cp\u003eNew year, new you, new skin routine! Kickstart 2022 with perfect-for-you products designed to keep your darling skin moisture-rich and glowy. In the Fresh Start box, you’ll find a hydrating oil serum, a toner that will give you a dewy complexion, a mask featuring hyaluronic acid as the superstar ingredient, a powerful vitamin C eye serum, and a creamy matte blush to give a subtle sheen to your ultra-hydrated skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFranklin \u0026amp; Whitman: Vitamin C Eye Serum\u003c\/strong\u003e ($39.95 value) \u003cbr\u003eNot all heroes wear capes. If you’ve got dark under-eye circles, then this serum is to the rescue with a concentrated vitamin C formula that reduces discoloration over time and boosts the appearance of collagen-rich skin. Powerhouse ingredients like moringa oil join the action to soothe while squalane smooths out fine lines.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eJubel Naturals: Daily Dew\u003c\/strong\u003e ($34 value) \u003cbr\u003eGive your skin its daily due of hydration with a luxurious blend of nutrient-rich oils formulated for skin on the drier side (but works great for all skin types, too). A dollop a day of this subtly-scented elixir will give you a supple glow, leaving your skin fresh as morning dew.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eRosatyque: Hyaluronic Acid Moisturizing Mask\u003c\/strong\u003e ($6 value) \u003cbr\u003eDip into the fountain of youth with this hydrating mask. Hyaluronic acid helps skin retain moisture while astragalus membranaceus root extract turns back the clock with its revered age-defying properties. Formulated to also address eczema, rashes, plus deliver a dose of antioxidants, this mask is a great use of your time and money.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSukin: Hydrating Mist Toner\u003c\/strong\u003e ($2.99) \u003cbr\u003eYou lead a busy life, and so does your skin. With this mist toner you can give your skin a little pick me up any time of the day or night. Chamomile and rosewater soothe and purify tired skin, and a couple spritzes after makeup application will give you a dewy complexion. Don’t spend another day without it.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePeek Beauty: Metalimatte Quick Drying Blush\u003c\/strong\u003e ($18.50 value) \u003cbr\u003eThink you can’t be subtle and striking all at once? Think again with this blush that gives you the best of all worlds. Starting as a smooth matte cream that finishes as a gorgeous powder, this blush, in shade Ku, is blended with a touch of metallic shimmer to give the perfect light to your look.\u003c\/p\u003e"}
  </script>

  

