</div><div id="shopify-section-16155774770aa11fbf" class="shopify-section homepage-section--faq-wrapper section--kinder-founders-wrapper"><div class="faqs homepage-sections-wrapper homepage-sections-wrapper--white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12 col-md-8 offset-md-2">
        <div class="faqs__header">
          <div class="subheader">
            questions?
          </div>
          <h2 class="underline--brush">
            Check Out Our FAQs
          </h2>
        </div>
          
<div id="how-does-the-subscription-service-work" class="faq faq--closed faq--even">
            <button type="button" class="faq__question btn--link" aria-label="Toggle answer">
              <span class="faq__question-text">How does the subscription service work?</span>
              <span class="faq__question-icon">

                <svg class="icon--kinder-minus" width="26" height="4" viewbox="0 0 26 4" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<rect x="0.428223" width="25" height="4" fill="#E3BDAB"/>
</svg>

                <svg class="icon--kinder-plus" width="25" height="26" viewbox="0 0 25 26" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<path d="M24.9782 15.45V11.1H15.0782V0.899998H10.4282V11.1H0.528223V15.45H10.4282V25.65H15.0782V15.45H24.9782Z" fill="#E3BDAB"/>
</svg>


              </span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq__answer rte"><p>Choose any of our subscription plans (Monthly, 3-Month, or 6-Month) and your first monthly box, our introductory <a href="/web/20220227111207/https://kinderbeauty.com/pages/whats-in-your-kinder-faves-box" target="_blank" title="What’s in Your Kinder Faves Box?">Kinder Faves Collection</a>, will ship within 3-4 days. <br/><br/>The following month we’ll start billing you* for your monthly shipments on the 8th of each month and ship your package out of our warehouse around the 15th. You’ll always receive a shipping confirmation email once your box leaves the warehouse.</p><p><em>*If you are signed up for a 3-Month or 6-Month planned, you&#x27;ll only be billed again at the end of your term.</em></p>
</div>
          </div>
        

          
<div id="what-comes-in-my-monthly-box" class="faq faq--closed faq--odd">
            <button type="button" class="faq__question btn--link" aria-label="Toggle answer">
              <span class="faq__question-text">What comes in my monthly box?</span>
              <span class="faq__question-icon">

                <svg class="icon--kinder-minus" width="26" height="4" viewbox="0 0 26 4" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<rect x="0.428223" width="25" height="4" fill="#E3BDAB"/>
</svg>

                <svg class="icon--kinder-plus" width="25" height="26" viewbox="0 0 25 26" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<path d="M24.9782 15.45V11.1H15.0782V0.899998H10.4282V11.1H0.528223V15.45H10.4282V25.65H15.0782V15.45H24.9782Z" fill="#E3BDAB"/>
</svg>


              </span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq__answer rte"><p>Each monthly box has more than $85 worth of products, with at least two of those items being full-sized. <br/><br/>The products we curate can be skincare, haircare, makeup, body products, and/or accessories.<br/><br/>We work hard to always provide the highest quality products, great variety, and unparalleled value for our subscribers.<br/><br/>And, of course, everything is always 100% vegan, cruelty-free, and clean!</p>
</div>
          </div>
        

          
<div id="are-all-products-vegan-and-cruelty-free" class="faq faq--closed faq--even">
            <button type="button" class="faq__question btn--link" aria-label="Toggle answer">
              <span class="faq__question-text">Are all products vegan and cruelty free?</span>
              <span class="faq__question-icon">

                <svg class="icon--kinder-minus" width="26" height="4" viewbox="0 0 26 4" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<rect x="0.428223" width="25" height="4" fill="#E3BDAB"/>
</svg>

                <svg class="icon--kinder-plus" width="25" height="26" viewbox="0 0 25 26" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<path d="M24.9782 15.45V11.1H15.0782V0.899998H10.4282V11.1H0.528223V15.45H10.4282V25.65H15.0782V15.45H24.9782Z" fill="#E3BDAB"/>
</svg>


              </span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq__answer rte"><p>Absolutely, yes! Our three founders are all long-time vegan and animal activists, who personally ensure that each chosen product goes through a strict vetting process to guarantee that every product we send your way has not been tested on animals and doesn&#x27;t contain any nasty animal ingredients or byproducts.</p>
</div>
          </div></div>
        
</div>

		
